Meet Some Sourcers
ServiceSource is an innovator in customer renewal, engagement and expansion solutions making it one of the industry’s most exciting places to work. But don’t take our word for it; let our employees tell you.






 



Leigh Underwood
Global Senior Program Manager
Leigh has 20 years of professional service experience with large complex global organizations in program management roles and works in our Nashville office.







 



Leon Harden
Recruiting
Manager
Leon started in 2015 and has been our Recruiting Manager for all of our General and Administrative positions based in our Denver office.  







 



Laura Smith
Channel Engagement Specialist
Laura started as a Sales Rep with us back in 2011 and most recently was promoted to Channel Engagement Specialist in our Liverpool office.







 



Jefferey Lim
Talent Acquisition
Lead
Jeff started with us a few months ago as a Talent Acquisition Lead and quickly has become a spokesperson and ambassador for ServiceSource in Kuala Lumpur.






