What's Your Passion
Explore the amazing career opportunities at ServiceSource.






 



InsideSales
Selling is the core of our business services. Our Inside Sales Representatives will help uncover new revenue opportunities and achieve meaningful results for some of the most recognized companies in the world.







 



Customer Service
Do you like helping companies drive engagement and the value of their products and services? Our customer support teams help do this though client health checks and assisting our sales teams identify growth opportunities.
 






 



Information Technology
Our Information Technology team helps to implement innovative solutions for both our internal and external clients. We strive to find, create and share services, tools and training to meet the unique needs of the company.







 



ProfessionalServices
We are on the front line with our clients to deliver powerful customer renewal, engagement and expansion solutions.  This creates opportunities for Engagement Managers, Solution Architects and Data Specialists.






