ServiceSource Fun Facts



 



Asia


In our brand new office in Singapore (we just had our Grand Opening in August!), we have 184 employees.
Kuala Lumpur has 647 employees and there is an employee bus from our site to the central station.
Our Yokahama office, with 62 employees is within walking distance of the Cosmo Clock 21 Ferris Wheel.





 



Philippines


Our 255 employees are located in one of the newest buildings in BGC.
The on-site health clinic in the building is managed by the esteemed St. Luke’s.
Come visit our brand new recruiting center on the 32nd floor.





 



North America


Three of our North America offices are strategically located right in the heart of downtown.
We have 388 employees in Denver, 722 in Nashville and 108 in SF/Seattle.
Our Nashville office started 8 years ago with 30 expansion employees (now it’s 722!).





 



Europe


The Liverpool office is right on the River Mersey and has 276 employees.
The Dublin office with its 301 employees is served by the famous Luas Green Line Tram.
Our Sophia office has 49 employees and is located in the tallest building in Bulgaria.





