   ServiceSource is hoping to bring a sense of renewal to its clients. Part sales professional staffer, part software developer, ServiceSource offers sales staff outsourcing and proprietary customer management software geared toward increasing sales contract renewals. Its software, which includes data management platforms and cloud applications, aggregates customer data from its clients' different enterprise systems (e.g. CRM, billing, order management) to facilitate customer management and analysis from a single, online location. Serving clients primarily in the technology sector, ServiceSource often markets its sales professionals in tandem with its software offerings.
  







